><br />\n<br />\n如果個女仔本身好嘅 根本無人理佢係唔係二灘 <br />\n如果個女仔本身差都要娶佢<br />\n咁係佢自己攞嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74665b66b1e06993ae768faf2552b4ceedf85942","tid":462550,"uid":120850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:01:11.000Z","msg":"所以識玩一定係大大頂綠帽笠落你班傻仔度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2609cd4d1ad0a4c43e4038ed0893a442542dc47a","tid":462550,"uid":84581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:04:47.000Z","msg":"我明 :("},{"pid":"4473a06c7b00b345d1dacbf84ca00f77a9241577","tid":462550,"uid":120399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:31:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>過來人<br />\n最慘係自己親眼見到...嗰個畫面係腦海揮之不去&hellip;依家出街見到七人車都勾返起嗰日嘅情景<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打分享吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你見佢上其他人車？<br />\n我係見住佢拖另一個隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你痛啲喎，見住佢拖第二個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我嗰case係我等佢，佢扮見唔到我，然後一路跑，最終跑上一個我唔識嘅男人車度，然後我再無見過佢.....<br />\n不過除咗依一幕，佢講嘅說話都好傷我，eg 就算係天堂都唔會再見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca0069ca15743c483af5e0bb8151c0d54611189","tid":462550,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:35:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"efa96ed8ccfb303c9f04e9255b321804be7d638d","tid":462550,"uid":66514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:38:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得戴總好過啲毒撚連機會都無"},{"pid":"198a413667c720ac9ce594a0e035be11cb0aea4d","tid":462550,"uid":152633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:48:07.000Z","msg":"戴帽係好痛苦的事 但時間會沖淡一切<br />\n信我啦偷食同俾綠帽人戴個啲都會有報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n將來佢一定會後悔失去你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf8dd2a8678364dedfe84337561fa4348de9485","tid":462550,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:21:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>過來人<br />\n最慘係自己親眼見到...嗰個畫面係腦海揮之不去&hellip;依家出街見到七人車都勾返起嗰日嘅情景<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打分享吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你見佢上其他人車？<br />\n我係見住佢拖另一個隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你痛啲喎，見住佢拖第二個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我嗰case係我等佢，佢扮見唔到我，然後一路跑，最終跑上一個我唔識嘅男人車度，然後我再無見過佢.....<br />\n不過除咗依一幕，佢講嘅說話都好傷我，eg 就算係天堂都唔會再見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你發夢會唔會見返依一幕？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係好痛，果時仲要我生日果幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢無理過我，個天咁都要俾我見到<br />\n果種痛苦真係非筆墨能形容<br />\n我到宜家都好記得果時嘅情景<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53064a4bc87c3981fcbaf8238deb0823376ae6ae","tid":462550,"uid":30710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:21:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以識玩一定係大大頂綠帽笠落你班傻仔度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不要玩弄人心"},{"pid":"6791f357e541d994b2c69943d20e9a024cb0644d","tid":462550,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:22:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>時間沖淡一切啊巴打</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝你巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36562a544fe292a25c027776b6d5aa4125b67e94","tid":462550,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:22:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得戴總好過啲毒撚連機會都無</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁咖咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我寧願無俾人傷害過喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed044809b7cb5fdcfd4a9b003f1734b8c8185ac4","tid":462550,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:23:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戴帽係好痛苦的事 但時間會沖淡一切<br />\n信我啦偷食同俾綠帽人戴個啲都會有報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n將來佢一定會後悔失去你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係咪有故事分享？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d7f6c11c88436a01332acc6c2cd75be7574df68","tid":462550,"uid":152244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:23:49.000Z","msg":"小事啦。我當年訓街食垃圾，乜都試過。宜家雖然都唔係過得舒服，但都活得自己開心"},{"pid":"e3d4518dcfafc91bc58443d57feefc80b98ae955","tid":462550,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:24:31.000Z","msg":"sor9ry 囉, <br />\n<br />\n淨係會知俾帽人戴係有幾爽  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d62d533462fd5c77b574ac836363dcce7b5775","tid":462550,"uid":152633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:32:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>戴帽係好痛苦的事 但時間會沖淡一切<br />\n信我啦偷食同俾綠帽人戴個啲都會有報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n將來佢一定會後悔失去你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係咪有故事分享？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對方去外國讀書 拍左兩年幾 <br />\n同佢分手唔夠兩星期佢就有新女... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42aa37dcecd109730c3087aed75b185330a53603","tid":462550,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:50:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>過來人<br />\n最慘係自己親眼見到...嗰個畫面係腦海揮之不去&hellip;依家出街見到七人車都勾返起嗰日嘅情景<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打分享吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你見佢上其他人車？<br />\n我係見住佢拖另一個隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你痛啲喎，見住佢拖第二個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我嗰case係我等佢，佢扮見唔到我，然後一路跑，最終跑上一個我唔識嘅男人車度，然後我再無見過佢.....<br />\n不過除咗依一幕，佢講嘅說話都好傷我，eg 就算係天堂都唔會再見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你發夢會唔會見返依一幕？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係好痛，果時仲要我生日果幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢無理過我，個天咁都要俾我見到<br />\n果種痛苦真係非筆墨能形容<br />\n我到宜家都好記得果時嘅情景<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比你見到好過佢𠵱家仲喺度瞞住你<br />\n樓上講得啱 最緊要除得快<br />\n𠵱家就等時間過"},{"pid":"7eff4f0d48cd4fc1282d4eea3d6798a33804b532","tid":462550,"uid":120399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T23:19:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>過來人<br />\n最慘係自己親眼見到...嗰個畫面係腦海揮之不去&hellip;依家出街見到七人車都勾返起嗰日嘅情景<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打分享吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你見佢上其他人車？<br />\n我係見住佢拖另一個隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你痛啲喎，見住佢拖第二個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我嗰case係我等佢，佢扮見唔到我，然後一路跑，最終跑上一個我唔識嘅男人車度，然後我再無見過佢.....<br />\n不過除咗依一幕，佢講嘅說話都好傷我，eg 就算係天堂都唔會再見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你發夢會唔會見返依一幕？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係好痛，果時仲要我生日果幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢無理過我，個天咁都要俾我見到<br />\n果種痛苦真係非筆墨能形容<br />\n我到宜家都好記得果時嘅情景<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者嗰內容有唔同，但都離不開女方、個第三者、部七人車同護士依4樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁你都幾慘，嗰次真係一個最難忘嘅生日"},{"pid":"705b3d368205e75051b5e3d421576e2a03729977","tid":462550,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T01:48:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>過來人<br />\n最慘係自己親眼見到...嗰個畫面係腦海揮之不去&hellip;依家出街見到七人車都勾返起嗰日嘅情景<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打分享吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你見佢上其他人車？<br />\n我係見住佢拖另一個隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile